| **Vulnerability type** | Remote code execution (RCE) through unauthenticated access to the web‑UI |
| **CVE** | CVE‑2024‑xxxx (publicly disclosed) |
| **Impact** | An attacker who can reach the PMP web‑UI can execute arbitrary code with the privileges of the PMP service account, potentially compromising the entire control‑system network. |
