| **Mitigation** | 1. Apply the 4.2.1 patch or later. 2. Disable or delete the default “admin” account. 3. Enforce MFA for all PMP users. 4. Restrict network access to the PMP web‑UI to a narrow CIDR block or VPN. 5. Enable logging and monitor for failed login attempts. 6. Verify the integrity of the patch with the vendor‑supplied SHA‑256 checksum. |

